âœ… AI-Powered Treatment Recommendations â€“ Provides disease-specific solutions.
âœ… User-Friendly UI â€“ Designed with Figma & developed using React.
âœ… Fast & Scalable Backend â€“ Built with FastAPI & MySQL for real-time responses.
âœ… Offline Mode â€“ Supports functionality without an internet connection.

